{
  "stem": "13315.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He mistreated everybody as much as he could.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, that was in another room.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "See, there were-- four-- in a block, there were three or four separate room.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Actually it was two rooms.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The one where you ate, and the other one where you slept.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Half the time we slept on straw on the floor.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't remember any names from there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "About 4 o'clock in the morning.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Had to wash up a little bit, get ready.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then stand for appel-- it was a roll call.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had to be there on the main square, regardless of whether it's 6 o'clock in the morning, the roll call.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then after the roll call, we went back for breakfast.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- and everywhere along the wall of the camp, were towers where there was always an SS man with machine gun.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was at freedom to shoot.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Nobody would control him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We saw once a shot man-- they intentionally led us by the corpse.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They said he tried to escape, which was ridiculous.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "How could he escape?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But they sometimes did to create a means of scaring the other people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The first one to walk towards a fence, and then they shot him because-- escape.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You couldn't escape there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was all surrounded by the SS troops.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, it was on top of it, yes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it was mainly these barbed wires.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And strong wiring.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the also a trench with water.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nothing, just empty field.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was wide-- in the-- it was farm country-- wide open fields.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't even see the SS vacations because they were on the other side.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Even though when you went out, then you saw them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But when you were in the camp, you didn't see them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Walking, then from the beginning, singing.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
